      "height": 145,
      "text": "shared.contacts\n──────────────────────────────────\nid UUID PK\nname TEXT\nroles TEXT[] DEFAULT '{}'\n  (e.g. ['owner'])\nentity_id UUID → memory entity graph\ncreated_at, updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n──────────────────────────────────\nUNIQUE INDEX: owner singleton\n  WHERE 'owner' = ANY(roles)",
