    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "mailbox_metrics_module_text",
      "x": 1860,
      "y": 2720,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "Mailbox Module\n─────────────────────────\nmailbox\n  id UUID PK\n  sender TEXT, sender_channel TEXT\n  subject TEXT, body TEXT\n  priority INTEGER\n  status TEXT  (unread/read/archived)\n  metadata JSONB\n  read_at, archived_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n\nMetrics Module\n─────────────────────────\nNo dedicated table.\nMetric definitions stored in state KV\n  under metrics_catalogue: prefix.\n  (max 1,000 per butler)\nPrometheus exposition via /metrics\nendpoint at runtime.",
      "originalText": "Mailbox Module\n─────────────────────────\nmailbox\n  id UUID PK\n  sender TEXT, sender_channel TEXT\n  subject TEXT, body TEXT\n  priority INTEGER\n  status TEXT  (unread/read/archived)\n  metadata JSONB\n  read_at, archived_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n\nMetrics Module\n─────────────────────────\nNo dedicated table.\nMetric definitions stored in state KV\n  under metrics_catalogue: prefix.\n  (max 1,000 per butler)\nPrometheus exposition via /metrics\nendpoint at runtime.",
