    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "isolation_text",
      "x": 2390,
      "y": 2718,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 390,
      "text": "Each butler role:\n  GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE,\n  DELETE, TRIGGER, REFERENCES\n  ON own schema\n\n  GRANT SELECT only\n  ON shared schema\n\n  REVOKE ALL\n  ON all other butler schemas\n\nsearch_path = own_schema,\n              shared, public\n\nInter-butler communication:\n  MCP-only through Switchboard\n  (no direct cross-schema queries)\n\nOwner contact bootstrapped\nautomatically on daemon startup\n(unique partial index enforces\n at most one owner contact)\n\nAlembic Migration Management:\n  Central: alembic/versions/core/\n  Per-butler: roster/{butler}/\n    migrations/\n  Module paths: src/butlers/\n    modules/{module}/migrations/\n  Dynamic schema targeting\n  at runtime",
      "originalText": "Each butler role:\n  GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE,\n  DELETE, TRIGGER, REFERENCES\n  ON own schema\n\n  GRANT SELECT only\n  ON shared schema\n\n  REVOKE ALL\n  ON all other butler schemas\n\nsearch_path = own_schema,\n              shared, public\n\nInter-butler communication:\n  MCP-only through Switchboard\n  (no direct cross-schema queries)\n\nOwner contact bootstrapped\nautomatically on daemon startup\n(unique partial index enforces\n at most one owner contact)\n\nAlembic Migration Management:\n  Central: alembic/versions/core/\n  Per-butler: roster/{butler}/\n    migrations/\n  Module paths: src/butlers/\n    modules/{module}/migrations/\n  Dynamic schema targeting\n  at runtime",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#991b1b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
